<% next_month = date.advance(months: 1) %>
<% publish_by = find_middle_day(next_month.change(day: 14), day: "Friday") %>
<% published_on = next_month.end_of_month + 1.day %>

<% if service.owner %>
Dear <%= service.owner.first_name %>
<% end %>

This is a reminder to provide performance data about <%= service.name %> for the period 1 to <%= date.end_of_month.day%> <%= date.to_formatted_s(:month_and_year) %>.

​You can enter your data here: <%= url %>

Please provide your data by <%= publish_by.to_formatted_s(:long_day_month_year) %>. It will be published on your service page on <%= published_on.to_formatted_s(:long_day_month_year) %>.

If the data isn’t provided by then, your service page will be published with missing data.

If you have any queries about this request ​please raise a Zendesk ticket ​by emailing publish-data@digital.cabinet-office.gov.uk

​Regards,
Service Performance team
